<br>
======================================================================<br>
<br>
OK first I'd like to thank you all for giving your time, guys, I know you work hard and it's good of you to invite a former preacher like me to talk to you.  I appreciate the work you have put into this game and especially the time you have spent working on the classes.  I think we all realize how difficult it is to balance a game like this and you have spent a great deal of time on it.<br>
<br>
And on Wizards, I imagine you'd have a tough time finding a way to balance a cannon like they are with your idea of how the game should be.  And I see now you are working on making Wizards more valuable in groups... in Velious... without working on damage, and we all appreciate the effort.  I just have one teeny tiny little minute itty bitty question I'd like to ask you...<br>
<br>
WHAT ABOUT THE DAMAGE!  WIZARDS ARE THE MASTERS OF MAGICAL DAMAGE, NOT THE MASTERS OF PORTING AROUND LIKE A PUNK BITCH TAXI!!!  NOBODY SIGNED ON TO TELEPORT AROUND AND NOT GET IN GROUPS!!!  NOT TO BUFF OR DEBUFF!!!  WHERE'S THE DAMAGE!!!!!  OHHH OHHHH!!!!!<br>
<br>
==================================================================<br>
<br>
Oh well he did it better than me, that's why he was a world famous comedian and I'm just a guy.  Course, Im still alive...<br>
<br>
Seriously though, fixing our non-damage grouping ability in Velious sounds an awful lot to me like Absor bought into the crappy lie that Wizards are fine until high level Velious encounters.  I am so SICK of seeing them pretend the class starts at level 35 and now they are even limiting it more to just Velious?  What is this?  I swear when ya think you've seen it all, I'd rather they did NOTHING than pull some crap like this. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www,kestrelarts.com/images/book.jpg BORDER=0> at: 5/11/01 6:22:50 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyaldin111.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yaldin111</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/10/01 9:23:22 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sam Kinison and the Verant Live Team</span><hr size=1> A fine tribute to a fine comedian...next write a rant about how female wood elves shouldn't be so scantily clad (=<br>
